<div id="review_2690991084" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2690991084" />
    <a title="Veronica-Anne" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/89192064-veronica-anne"><img alt="Veronica-Anne" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1542165799p2/89192064.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2690991084?book_show_action=true">Jan 28, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Veronica-Anne" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Veronica-Anne" href="/user/show/89192064-veronica-anne">Veronica-Anne</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/18592434-brain">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2690991084" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13072977464446579555">Robin Cook is an exceptional writer of the thriller/horror genre. Tension is always presents as the story builds into a terrifying climax. Using his medical knowledge to create horror in an specialized field that is trusted so openly, he wields a tale so frighteningly real that it makes you question the world of medicine in general. I could not put this book down. It was that good. Highly recommended.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


