              <span id="reviewTextContainer3376377552" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8825474732822053668">Not bad for one of his older books, but not great either. I thought he wrote the suspense very well and he does a great job at making the reader feel what a nervous patient feels. However, the techncial medical details throughout the novel were a bit more extensive than necessary for storytelling purposes. </span>

